***************Risk Identification/assessment

Nessus(Tool)


*************** Penetration Testing(Pen Testing) - Check vulnerabilities assessment

*************** Threat assessment - define the threat 
1. Adversial - hacker, malware, someone doing naughty in your infrastructure
2. Accidental - type something to get wrong
3. Structural - Power supply, monitor or camera. Equipment or software failure.
4. Environmental - fire, earthquake, etc.


*************** Risk Response
Mitigation - is effort to reduce impact of risk.
